<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='928760' id='t-928760'>that no one of us is as smart as all of us thinking together.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='933382' id='t-933382'>No one person, no one alliance, no one nation,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='937042' id='t-937042'>no one of us is as smart as all of us thinking together.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
