<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='941823' id='t-941823'>The vision statement of Wikipedia is very simple:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='946505' id='t-946505'>a world in which every human being can freely share</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='949619' id='t-949619'>in the sum of all knowledge.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='951252' id='t-951252'>My thesis for you is that by combining international,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='955730' id='t-955730'>interagency, private-public, strategic communication,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='959900' id='t-959900'>together, in this 21st century,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='963365' id='t-963365'>we can create the sum of all security.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
